The former Ekiti state governor, Peter Ayodele Fayose, birthday is today. Ayo Fayose, as he his fondly called, came into the spotlight of politics during his tenure as a sitting governor of Ekiti and remains relevant in politics after being succeeded by Kayode Fayemi. The politician has brought us to laughter with some of his antics and also challenged the status quo in Ekiti. Below are notable events in the life of Ayo Fayose has he turns fifty-seven years today: